FBIS4-43756 "drweu119_q_94008" FBIS-WEU-94-119 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 TURKEY Bomb Explosions, Casualties Reported Bomb Explosions, Casualties Reported Twelve Injured at Festival NC1606143094 Istanbul TERCUMAN in Turkish 14 Jun 94 p 7 NC1606143094 Istanbul TERCUMAN Turkish BFN [Report by Hulya Metin] [Excerpt] This year's 30th Cherry Festival in Tekirdag turned into a bloodbath. A bomb exploded at Tarsal tourist installations where a part of the festival was being held. Twelve persons were injured, one of them seriously. No one was killed. The explosion, which occurred at Tarsal's cocktail lounge at 2115, created a great panic at the crowded beach. The police officials said it was a fragmentation bomb and that investigation into the case is continuing. No organization has yet assumed responsibility. [passage omitted]
